  "_hooks_explanation": "Hooks intentionally NOT configured at the team level yet. Pre-commit framework (.pre-commit-config.yaml) handles formatting + linting on commit; CI (.github/workflows/ci.yml) handles full test/lint/type runs on push. Adding PostToolUse hooks that auto-format on every Edit creates subtle race conditions where Claude reads a file, edits it, the hook reformats it, and Claude's next view doesn't match its last write. We can revisit if specific friction emerges. Personal hooks can be added in settings.local.json.",
  "hooks": {}
